<servinfo servinfosgmlid = "AHRAP70A4106019" svcinfotypenbr = "08" svcinfoqualnbr = "03" page = "2" supplyoff = "1" modify = "0">
<title>
Pregled sklopa glavnog cilindra kočnice
</title>
<ptxt>
<intxrefpoff refid = "AHRAP70A4106017">Uklanjanje i ugradnja sklopa glavnog cilindra kočnice</intxrefpoff>
</ptxt>
<attention2>
<ptxt>
Nakon pregleda, obavezno isperite kočnu tekućinu sa specijalnog alata. Kočna tekućina koja ostane na specijalnom alatu može ga oštetiti.
</ptxt>
</attention2>
<servinfosub id = "AHRAP70A4106019001">
<title>
Pregled bez opterećenja
</title>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Postavite specijalni alat u kanal na primarnoj strani (1) kako je ispod prikazano.
</ptxt>
<attention3>
<ptxt>
Ako vozilo nije opremljeno ESP<sup>®</sup>-om, specijalni alat (C) ne koristi se za ovaj pregled.
</ptxt>
</attention3>
<servicetool>
<servicetoolitem id = "L4A006">
<s-part>
(A)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09918-78211">
09918-78211
</s-number>
<ptxt>
</ptxt>
</servicetoolitem>
<servicetoolitem id = "L4A007">
<s-part>
(B)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09952-46010">
09952-46010
</s-number>
<ptxt>
</ptxt>
</servicetoolitem>
<servicetoolitem id = "L4A008">
<s-part>
(C)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09952-48010">
09952-48010
</s-number>
<ptxt>
</ptxt>
</servicetoolitem>
</servicetool>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "IAP70A410017.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "48.434mm" ver = "01" gw = "186" gh = "121"/>
<callout>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<tgroup cols = "4" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<colspec colnum = "1" colname = "1" colwidth = "0.315in"/>
<colspec colnum = "2" colname = "2" colwidth = "1.105in"/>
<colspec colnum = "3" colname = "3" colwidth = "0.315in"/>
<colspec colnum = "4" colname = "4" colwidth = "1.644in"/>
<tbody>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" align = "right">
<ptxt>
2.
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Sekundarni kanal
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "3" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" align = "right">
<ptxt>
3.
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "4" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
Sklop glavnog cilindra kočnice
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</callout>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Specijalnim alatom (A) primijenite pritisak na sklop glavnog cilindra kočnice i potvrdite da u cilindru ne raste tlak.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Ako tlak raste, sklop glavnog cilindra kočnice je oštećen i mora se zamijeniti.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Ponovite 1. i 2. korak i za kanal na sekundarnoj strani.
</ptxt>
</s1>
</servinfosub>
<servinfosub id = "AHRAP70A4106019002">
<title>
Pregledajte nepropusnost zraka
</title>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Sa sklopom glavnog cilindra kočnice (1) pričvršćenim na škripac (2) kako je dolje prikazano, postavite specijalni alat u kanal na primarnoj strani.
</ptxt>
<attention3>
<ptxt>
Prilikom uporabe škripca, stavite čistu krpu između glavnog cilindra kočnice i škripca kako ne biste oštetili glavni cilindar kočnice.
</ptxt>
</attention3>
<servicetool>
<servicetoolitem id = "L4A009">
<s-part>
(A)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09918-78211">
09918-78211
</s-number>
<ptxt>
</ptxt>
</servicetoolitem>
<servicetoolitem id = "L4A010">
<s-part>
(B)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09952-46010">
09952-46010
</s-number>
<ptxt>
</ptxt>
</servicetoolitem>
<servicetoolitem id = "L4A011">
<s-part>
(C)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09952-48010">
09952-48010
</s-number>
<ptxt>
</ptxt>
</servicetoolitem>
</servicetool>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "IAP70A410015.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "57.703mm" ver = "01" gw = "192" gh = "147"/>
<callout>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<tgroup cols = "2" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<colspec colnum = "1" colname = "1" colwidth = "0.315in"/>
<colspec colnum = "2" colname = "2" colwidth = "1.873in"/>
<tbody>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" align = "right">
<ptxt>
“a”:
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" align = "left">
<ptxt>
50 mm (2,0 in)
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</callout>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Specijalnim alatom primijenite tlak od 50 kPa (0,5 kgf/cm<sup>2</sup>, 7,25 psi, 0,5 bar) na sklop glavnog cilindra kočnice.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Ako tlak ne raste, sklop glavnog cilindra kočnice je oštećen i mora se zamijeniti.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Ponovite 1. i 2. korak za kanal na sekundarnoj strani.
</ptxt>
</s1>
</servinfosub>
</servinfo>
</servinfotype>
